<br>
In this building is were the casters reside.  on the far wall as you enter it there is a banner hanging with a guard standing to either side of it.  Click on the banner and it will take you up to the second floor, click it again and you will go to the 3rd floor, click again and you will go to the 4th floor.  on the 4th floor click the banner again and you will appear at the doors that you went through to enter the building.  It is on the 3rd floor that i found the merchants for the verious casters that sold all research spells <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> EXCEPT</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> they did not carry the highest level research spells. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uvashanti.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vashanti</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.tampabay.rr.com/eqsite/bullet3.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Banner Sculptor</span><br>  Posts: 81<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 11:27:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1052.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.tampabay.rr.com/eqsite/Vashanti/VashNoggin_Anim.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: That name</span><hr size=1> I couldn't find the Enchanter research spells I was looking for in the spellcaster area of Katta Castellum, but I found the Wizard ones <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p><p>
